title: Browns 1st Playoff TD in 18 Years Comes 14 Seconds into the Game
author: NFL
description:
A botched snap travels all the way into the end zone and Cleveland recovers for a touchdown! The Cleveland Browns take on the Pittsburgh Steelers during Super Wild Card Weekend of the 2020 NFL postseason.
